description: Mister No’s last client is certainly unusual! She is called Ethel Mazelbaum and she wants to fulfil her Grandfather’s dream: find a city lost in the jungle, established by rebel Incas. However, the city is coveted not only by Ethel, but also by the wicked merchant Bastos…
name: La Città Dimenticata

description: Finally Mister No and Ethel arrive in the lost city of the Inca leader Manoi-Capac, thanks to help from Mayta, an Indian priestess who is a descendant of the Incas. Bastos and his men follow them: but the city is full of lethal traps and only a fortunate few will survive!
name: Trappola di Pietra

description: Certain debts are a stone around one’s neck! Jerry meets Nat Doomey, who saved his life during the Second World War. Nat makes Mister No participate in the Pegasus project, organized by the American army to test a new aeroplane prototype for vertical takeoff. But some of the experts involved in the project sell out to “foreign powers”…
name: Progetto Pegasus

description: Leo Korda is a famous photo-reporter who has travelled the world. He wants to document “real Amazonia, the last paradise”, and Mister No leads him to the large village of Yanoama hidden in the heart of the forest. But a group of ruthless Garimpeiros also want to reach the tribe…
name: Razza Selvaggia

description: The Garimpeiros of the ruthless Hauser massacre a Yanoama tribe to gain possession of some gold nuggets. But Leo Korda takes photographs of the massacre. He and Mister No therefore become a prey hunted by the Garimpeiros who want to cancel all trace of their slaughter. But it is Jerry who will put his signature, albeit in a radically new way, on the epilogue of this tragedy…
name: Il Giorno degli Avvoltoi

description: Plants, Indios, animals… An entire universe is dying. Shocked, Mister No, does something extreme: together with Esse-Esse, he blows up the factory of the Brazil Chemical Company whose products were destroying the Amazon Forest. But among those who are financing the factory, there is an occult and powerful Japanese organisation. The mysterious Ishikawa leads the organisation and to get revenge he lays waste to Manaus. For Jerry things will never be the same again…
name: Vento Rosso

description: Mister No’s world has fallen apart. The Non- Living Legion, a secret Japanese organisation, is hunting him down and has killed some of his best friends (like the mechanic Augustino and maybe Esse-Esse! ) Jerry is a man on the run when he arrives in Natal on the Brazilian coast. He is wrecked, he is not the same man: but resurrection is possible…
name: Squali

description: In Natal, one of Ishikawa’s men, Tsuhiro, takes side with the Barras, the ruthless mobsters. But Mister No has met a doctor’s daughter, Shona, and has recovered his fighting spirit. But eliminating Tsuhiro will not be easy, also because another person has entered the scene, someone who was thought to be dead….
name: Il Sangue degli Eroi

description: Mister No, Esse-Esse and Shona are at sea on her dead father’s boat, fleeing from Ishikawa’a men. A hurricane forces them to take shelter on an island inhabited by a mysterious old man. And here Jerry will face his past…
name: L'Isola dei Giorni Perduti

description: Cuba. A Caribbean island oppressed by the dictatorship of Fulgencio Batista. Here Mister No, Esse-Esse, and Shona meet a mad Cuban General, a revolutionary artist and, above all, they get embroiled in the CIA’s obscure power politics…
name: Giochi Pericolosi

description: Todos Los Angeles. Mister No has himself shut away in this Mexican prison. One of the prisoners is a member of the Non-Living Legion, the Japanese organisation that is after him, and Jerry wants to interrogate him. But someone is double-dealing in the penitentiary…
name: Fuga dall'Inferno

description: In the cemetery of a small Mexican town, Hermanas, there is a mountain of money. And some criminals have found the fruits of a robbery on the body of one of their accomplices. One of the thugs, Pickens, comes back to get the booty, but his path crosses Mister No’s. What secret is the old cemetery guard, Enrique, hiding?
name: Il Segreto della Cripta

description:
"Pranks for the Memories": Can it be so? Is Reggie really throwing the comedic cosmos into chaos by completely abandoning April Fools' Day Pranks? What is this, some sort of a joke?!

"Teen Trauma": When it comes to his students, Mr. Weatherbee is a real problem-solver... but when they take up all his time, that leaves him with a problem of his own to solve!

"Poet Tree": Reggie thinks that he will never see a poem as lovely as a tree... unless it's about a lovely girl of course!

Reprint of Thor #1.
 
Not a clone! Not a robot! Not an imaginary story! The God of Thunder is officially BACK! You’ve waited for it, you’ve demanded it…and we say thee YEA! The Odinson comes roaring to life in this highly anticipated ongoing series by red-hot superstars J. Michael Straczynski (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) and Olivier Coipel (HOUSE OF M)! But how does a god return from Ragnarok? And what place will he find in a world torn by CIVIL WAR?
name: Rebirth
